<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><div><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for getting in touch with Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please accept this email as confirmation that&nbsp;<b>we have removed your policy from our renewal process</b>.&nbsp;</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>Your current policy is due to expire on&nbsp;<i>(add in expiry date)</i></b>.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>We’ll send automated emails to make sure you’re aware of your policy expiry date so that you can either renew your policy with us manually or find cover elsewhere to keep your business protected against claims.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Our renewals team may still get in touch with to check whether your circumstances have changed and you would like to renew this policy manually.&nbsp; &nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to get in touch.<br></span><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></font><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
